						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone built into the wall of the backyard of the Taluk Office.</hi></p>						

						<p>12th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription in Kannaḍa verse records that people mourned over the death of Kaṁpila and Siḍila-Bomma. It refers to <hi rend="italic">Dhavaḷaṁka-Bhīma,</hi> perhaps a title of Kaṁpila. In characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th Century.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
